<title>JAPAN: Chugai Mining plans third-party share allocation.</title>
<headline>Chugai Mining plans third-party share allocation.</headline>
<dateline>TOKYO 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Chugai Mining Co Ltd said on Friday that it plans to issue 75 million new shares in a third-party allocation, subject to the approval of a shareholders' meeting in June.</p>
<p>The issue price of the common shares would be 60 yen and the total issue amount 4.5 billion yen, the gold refiner said in a statement.</p>
<p>The payment date would be December 17, it said.</p>
